title: [Feywrot Mire, Spirit Way]
description: The path here grows narrow, nearly imperceptable in spots, waging a loosing battle with the prolific encroachment of skunk cabbage from all sides.  The dense, and not so fragrant, ground cover seems determined to renounce the right of passage from those who seek egress here.
